          },
          "reviewBody": "I am a part of this school right from K0, and right now I am in 10th. It is the best school in all aspects. I dont have words to express my gratitude towards SSRVM and to all the teachers right from K0 to 10th std who built my personality. A very special thanks to Amol Sir( Physical Training coach) for recognizing my potential in Athletics and also for believing in me and for providing many opportunities to prove myself. All my Achievements and progress in sports is a product of his accurate Guidance and Sacrifice. I also want to thank Mansi tr and Manju tr who were my class teachers in std 7,8,9 for allowing me to participate in various competitions and tournaments. A special thanks to Mandar Sir for giving me an opportunity to play Tasha in the Dhol Tasha Pathak. A big thanks to the 10th std teachers who put in a lot of hard work to make all the students successful.",
